reviewText: I couldn't pass up the price on 2 DVD's!  My girls love it - it's very sassy and fun.  The colors are bright and the characters are so cute.  Definately worth the money!

my daughter really loves these movies....she almost know all the words to it and she cast a spell on me all day.....
but i do think it could have been a little less scary, so many cartoons are so dark and scary....with witches and magic and spells.

but she love's it.
